title: Shebeen Live In Creggan
description:

Shebeen - Live In Creggan
Track List: The Sam Song, Long Kesh, Roll of Honour, Sean South, Billy Reid, God Save Ireland, Willie & Danny, Willie Maley/Fields of Athenry, Bring Them Home, Say Hello To The Provos, Go On Home British Soldiers.
